commit.message:
more whitespace changes from astyle

- add more semicolons after FILLME in tutorial to avoid strange
  indentation

use z_U-z_L to initialize y_c for fixed vars treated as constraints

- fixes #728

fix declaration of MA57 API for case of long integers (FUNNY_MA57_INT)

- use ma57int instead of ipindex
increase version to 3.14.14

update libhsl/coin-hsl prebuild packages description again

- at least libHSL already includes all dependencies
- Coin-HSL so far misses the header file to be used as buildtime, so
  it is essentially the same as libHSL (just smaller)
- both are only for macOS and Windows (for Linux, one would need to
  unpack a julia package; we skip mentioning that)
- see #721
juliahsl is now libhsl; coin-hsl now also has binaries; see #721
set 3.14.13 release date
update options.dox: new option added

fix typos in option docu

- taken from 02ce6153225e106e296980458499eb10b34b40ac

add possibility to append to output file instead of truncating

- add option file_append
- add default argument for file_append to various API functions
- closes #720
Extends MA27 insufficient memory error catching

run astyle

- and separate some variable declarations for pointer type for readability

update astyle command

- --add-brackets seems to have been replaced by --add-braces
fix some doxygen/javadoc issues
update Doxyfile to doxygen 1.9.8
check that dimension/counts from get_nlp_info are nonnegative, ref #717

initialize jacobian approx also if nz_full_jac_g is 0

- avoids dereference of NULL pointer later on if there are constraints
- having nz_full_jac_g=0, but m>0 is very likely a user error (#717)

Fix eval_jac_g error being silently ignored in TNLPAdapter::GetSpaces (#697)

- throw INVALID_NLP exception now
document workaround for using static mkl libs, from #694
note that OMP_NESTED no longer needs to be set

remove link to spral fork on lanl

- doesn't seem to be updated anymore
adapt to change from long to int64_t in spral structs
working link to Andreas' thesis
up version to 3.14.13
